title: [Android] Who's getting coffee
description:
Who's getting coffee ?

When simple tasks needs to be done within a group of people, there's often arguing.
This app aims to prevent that, by randomly picking a victim from a group of people.

Who's getting coffee is the random name picker. Pick a random victim that will bring the coffee, or anything else, to rest of the group. Simply list the participients, shuffle them, and get the 'winner'.
